User Manual for Lord of Space Game
Introduction
Welcome to "Lord of Space," a thrilling arcade-style shooter game where you navigate through the cosmos, battling against a variety of enemy species. Get ready to experience the excitement of space combat like never before!
Installation
To play "Lord of Space," you will need to have Java and JavaFX installed on your computer. Follow these steps to get started:
1.	Install Java: Ensure you have the latest version of Java installed. You can download it from the official Java website.
2.	Install JavaFX: Download and install JavaFX from OpenJFX.
3.	Download Game: Clone or download the game repository from GitHub (link provided by the game developer).
4.	Set Up JavaFX: Make sure to configure your IDE to include the JavaFX library in the project settings.
Running the Game
Once you have installed Java and JavaFX, you can run the game by executing the LordOfSpaceApp.java file in your IDE or using the command line:
java --module-path /path/to/javafx-sdk/lib --add-modules javafx.controls,javafx.fxml,javafx.graphics,javafx.media,javafx.swing,javafx.web -cp . LordOfSpaceApp 
Replace /path/to/javafx-sdk/lib with the actual path to the JavaFX library on your system.
Gameplay
•	Start Screen: When you launch the game, you will be greeted with a start screen where you can choose your spaceship. When you hover over each spaceship with your mouse a small backstory is provided for the user to read .Use your mouse to select one of the available ships.
•	Controls:
•	Move: Move your spaceship horizontally by moving your mouse left or right.
•	Shoot: Click the left mouse button to shoot at enemy ships.
•	Objective: Your goal is to destroy as many enemy ships as possible to increase your score. Avoid colliding with enemy ships and meteoroids.
•	Enemies: You will encounter various enemy species. Stay alert and adapt your strategy to survive.
•	Game Over: The game ends if your spaceship is hit by an enemy or a meteoroid. Your final score will be displayed on the screen.
Tips for Success
•	Keep moving to avoid enemy or meteoroid collisions.
•	Focus on taking down one enemy at a time.
•	Watch for patterns in enemy movements.
Conclusion
Thank you for playing "Lord of Space"! We hope you enjoy this action-packed journey through the stars. Good luck!
